* DONE Screenshots on prod — absolute API URL [frontend] :ARCHIVE:
CLOSED: [2026-04-19 Sun]
:PROPERTIES:
:ARCHIVE_TIME: 2026-04-23 Thu 20:06
:ARCHIVE_FILE: ~/Network/syncthing/Projects/career_caddy/todo.org
:ARCHIVE_OLPATH: Inbox
:ARCHIVE_CATEGORY: todo
:ARCHIVE_TODO: DONE
