* SHIPPED [#A] Sidebar + chat as universal slide-in panels [frontend]
:PROPERTIES:
:ARCHIVE_TIME: 2026-04-29 Wed 10:59
:ARCHIVE_FILE: ~/Network/syncthing/Projects/career_caddy/todo.org
